00:37:39,384 --> 00:37:41,304
At first I thought maybe
something scary would happen...

747
00:37:41,345 --> 00:37:45,395
like what happened with Danica
while she was kidnapped by a man...

748
00:37:45,432 --> 00:37:48,142
