00:39:11,268 --> 00:39:12,938
Grab it right in the middle.

768
00:39:17,482 --> 00:39:18,692
Okay. There.

769
00:39:18,734 --> 00:39:21,404
And go up, Jackie go down. You see it?

770
00:39:21,445 --> 00:39:22,455
Not yet.

771
00:39:22,487 --> 00:39:24,527
All right. Here.

772
00:39:25,449 --> 00:39:26,779
- How about now?
- No.

773
00:39:27,242 --> 00:39:28,952
Well you're going to.

774
00:39:28,994 --> 00:39:31,204
I don't see it yet, I mean...

775
00:39:35,501 --> 00:39:37,631
- You ready?
- Yeah.

776
00:39:44,718 --> 00:39:47,298
300 feet of continuous cotton loops.

777
00:39:47,721 --> 00:39:49,311
That's what I drew.

778
00:39:50,057 --> 00:39:54,477
This is why I would like to ask you
for your investment, Trudy.

779
00:39:55,646 --> 00:39:59,436
