00:47:24,595 --> 00:47:26,935
- What?
- Another bill from Gerhardt.

915
00:47:26,972 --> 00:47:29,722
This guy keeps billing me
for his mistakes.

916
00:47:29,766 --> 00:47:31,846
- That's business.
- No.

917
00:47:31,894 --> 00:47:33,694
That's not the way I do business.

918
00:47:33,729 --> 00:47:35,229
I'm calling this guy.

919
00:47:40,611 --> 00:47:42,701
Gerhardt, I'm not gonna
keep paying for these parts...

920
00:47:42,738 --> 00:47:44,358
that it's taking
you four times to get right.

