923
00:47:50,370 --> 00:47:52,750
My clients pay when we figure it out.

924
00:47:52,789 --> 00:47:54,459
It was not my design, Gerhardt.

925
00:47:54,499 --> 00:47:57,039
It was your mistake. I'm not paying it.

926
00:47:57,085 --> 00:47:59,625
That was your design.
You have to pay.

927
00:47:59,671 --> 00:48:01,591
Did you just hang up on him?

928
00:48:01,632 --> 00:48:05,092
This guy was supposed to be easy
and inexpensive.

929
00:48:05,135 --> 00:48:07,755
He keeps overbilling us.
