971
00:50:20,979 --> 00:50:23,149
I really like it. Can we buy it?

972
00:50:23,190 --> 00:50:24,610
Take it easy, Cristy.

973
00:50:24,942 --> 00:50:28,072
Wow. I mean, that's just amazing.
